name: The Best Revenge Is Massive Success
description:
The Edition
- Limited edition of 10 prints. 
- 01 signed, dated and unnumbered artist proof.
- Produced in January 2012.
- Dated, numbered and signed on the back.

The Print
- Hand pulled silkscreen over historical marbled paper pattern The French Shell.
- Quote by Frank Sinatra “The best revenge is massive success”.
- The marbled paper pattern was reproduced using the techniques, tools and some of the materials used in the production of the early marbled papers, during the 16th to 19th centuries.
- Paper Hahnemuhle Bugra, 130 gsm.
- Paper size is 100 x 80 cm
- Printed area: Marbled pattern 100 x 80 cm, Silkscreen quote 70 x 50 cm.
- Certificate of authenticity with information on the edition and details of its production printed on the back.
